  "description": "<p>\n\t有没有听说过这么一个笑话：道行高深、阴险毒辣的伏地魔，为什么除不掉哈利波特这么一个小屁孩？原因就是：伏地魔有&ldquo;拖延症&rdquo;！光是电影，就拍了10年&hellip;&hellip;</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">身在职场，</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">你是不是也深陷&ldquo;拖延症&rdquo;难以自拔呢？</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/33462?source=692\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201308/41e888f507574c6794672593e5dae72d.jpg\" /></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"background-color: #008000;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 什么是拖延症？ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: #008000;\">拖延症（Procrastination）</span>指的是非必要、后果有害的推迟行为。目前，这个词并不是一个严格的心理学或医学术语，但<strong>严重或经常的拖延行为，常常是一些深层问题的表现。</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t拖延现象现已成为管理学家和心理学家研究的一个重要课题。</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">另外，别以为&ldquo;拖延症&rdquo;是当代人才有的毛病哦，其实古而有之，否则怎么会有明代人创作的《明日歌》呢？</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"background-color: #008000;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;拖延症自测 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</strong></span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 0);\">&nbsp;以下选项，有一项符合计1分，不符合计0分</span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">1 上班时间总在网上瞎逛，快到下班才开始忙；</span><br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">2 总是&ldquo;伪加班&rdquo;，白天可做完的事，总是拖到下班后加班做；</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">3 要做事时，脑子里能冒出各种理由：现在先做别的事，这个稍后；　&nbsp;</span><br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">4 自我麻痹：还来得及，不行就通宵赶工；　　</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">5 懒散，日复一日总想着明天再做；</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">6 处理问题不分主次，忙了半天，最紧要的事没做；　</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">7 每当同事或上司询问工作进展时，经常说&ldquo;让我再看看，再调整一下&rdquo;；　</span><br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">8 团队合作时，同事都面露难色，不愿和你合作;　</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">9 厚脸皮，反正别人怎么催，也定力十足，习以为常了；</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">10 经常因为时间过于紧迫，草草交差，结果被同事或老板责怪；<br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">11 从不主动汇报工作。</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"display: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 0);\">测试结果如下：</span></span></strong></p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>得分在0~3分之间，</strong>轻度拖延正向你靠近！<span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\"><strong>得分在4~7分之间，</strong>中度拖延已经绊住了你！！</span></span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>得分在8~11分之间，</strong>重度拖延让你病入膏肓！！！</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 0);\"><strong style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\">亲，不要放弃治疗！&nbsp;</strong></span><a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/course/33462?source=692\" style=\"line-height: 1.8em;\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"试听\" src=\"http://res.c.hjfile.c